2. Case Studies: Deconstructing Approved LRA 27 Mutations

To fully understand the necessity of the VipimoAI engine, we must deconstruct real-world, Ardhisasa-
approved mutation workflows. These cases highlight the friction of manual drafting and the spatial reasoning

that VipimoAI is built to automate.
Case Study 1: The Precision Derivation & Transcription Trap

