5. The "Delta-Capture" ML Schema
This schema is designed to feed directly into a Machine Learning model by isolating the exact variables the
human surveyor changed.
Table Name Purpose
ai_baseline_proposals Records exactly what the Slide-Line Solver originally recommended.
human_override_events Records the specific actions the surveyor took (e.g., ROAD_WIDEN).
learning_deltas Background worker calculates exact mathematical differences to train the model per